      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图来展示IoT工业PLC逻辑的版本管理流程。核心场景是：从main分支cherry-pick一个关键提交到develop分支。标题就叫\"Cherry-pick from main (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
